    "description": "<strong>轰炸机小队的队员们，跟随我一起到游戏里去执行危险的任务，在天空中实现自己的价值，养成、策略、生存、胜利！</strong><br><br><strong>培养你的队员！</strong><br>按你的喜好来训练和打扮这些手下的队员。他们每一个人都有自己的名字、性格、特技，以及…过去的故事。但是一定要当心，他们真的会战死，不能复活那种。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/c9809f54ef9bd60b5f3c0d88a1fc39a1.poster.avif?t=1768471106\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/c9809f54ef9bd60b5f3c0d88a1fc39a1.webm?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/c9809f54ef9bd60b5f3c0d88a1fc39a1.mp4?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>二战轰炸机作战的完全模拟！</strong><br>从燃料、液压到弹药，你需要微操队员去进行这架二战轰炸机上面的一切行动。当然你也可以自定义这家飞机，用游戏内自带的工具给它添加各种个性的图层，给它画个小丑鼻子或许会震慑敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/b1c8985ac26f53ae23c33fe16ae6bbd1.poster.avif?t=1768471106\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/b1c8985ac26f53ae23c33fe16ae6bbd1.webm?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/b1c8985ac26f53ae23c33fe16ae6bbd1.mp4?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>即时策略和战术！</strong><br>每一个任务都可能要面对随时而来的危险。敌方的战机、高射炮，时晴时雨雷电交加的恶劣天气，甚至缺少氧气——只要飞机一升空，身边就会围绕着很多随时可能发生的不可控因素，需要你去实时地操控解决，并且合理安排时机。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/7bdbae149996facec1d67e551df92493.poster.avif?t=1768471106\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/7bdbae149996facec1d67e551df92493.webm?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/7bdbae149996facec1d67e551df92493.mp4?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>时刻准备着！</strong><br>有备而战是每一个任务成功的关键。在敌人发现你之前定位锁定他们，但即使是在最火热地交火的时候，也不要忘记你最重要的轰炸任务，让每一个小队队员都各司其职，死得其所…（呸呸呸）。要记住，在这架二战轰炸机上面，每一个细节的成功都是最终胜利的助推器！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/c2a8b751ea4d13d90c854eb29a61fe83.poster.avif?t=1768471106\" width=598 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/c2a8b751ea4d13d90c854eb29a61fe83.webm?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/537800/extras/c2a8b751ea4d13d90c854eb29a61fe83.mp4?t=1768471106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
